599
00:35:02,688 --> 00:35:04,315
É... Deve estar mesmo.

600
00:35:06,692 --> 00:35:08,694
Se houvesse tempo e
se eu estivesse forte o bastante,

601
00:35:09,486 --> 00:35:10,696
